lead_paragraph: Vontaze Burfict was having the game of his life when he ran into the bowels of Paul Brown Stadium with what appeared to be a clinching interception, trailed by Adam "Pacman" Jones and several teammates eager to celebrate.

headline.print_headline: Column: Bengals Pay the Price for Character of Players
